and source evidence for home/history/discovery presentation behaviors","status":"in_progress","priority":"high"},{"content":"Implement phase-04 home/history/discovery presentation behaviors in Foodike-Harmony","status":"pending","priority":"high"},{"content":"Run focused verification/build or documented reproduction within harness budget","status":"pending","priority":"medium"},{"content":"Update source coverage and platform capability authority records for completed groups","status":"pending","priority":"high"}],"truncated":false},"title":"4 todos","time":{"start":1782389090674,"end":1782389090675}},"id":"prt_efeab26aa001lRRhF2GtsQW710","sessionID":"ses_1015564daffeewn8Ynq2E7YoiC","messageID":"msg_efeab10df001iF3VAqm3kXUIon"}}
